water infrastructure from terrorist threats. The EPA is the designated lead agency for
protection of drinking water and water treatment systems. Under this directive:
􀂋 DHS and EPA should ensure that protection includes EMP attack among the recognized
threats to the water infrastructure.
􀂋 The following initiatives should be amended:
— The President’s National Strategy for the Physical Protection of Critical Infrastructures
